FBIS4-32861 "drlat104_m_94002" FBIS-LAT-94-104 Daily Report 30 May 1994 Brazil Minister Signs Tlatelolco Treaty in Mexico Minister Signs Tlatelolco Treaty in Mexico PY3105012194 Rio de Janeiro Rede Globo Television in Portuguese 2300 GMT 30 May 94 PY3105012194 Rio de Janeiro Rede Globo Television Portuguese BFN [Text] Brazil today signed the Tlatelolco Treaty, whereby our country commits itself to refraining from manufacturing nuclear bombs or weapons. Brazilian Foreign Minister Celso Amorim participated in the signing ceremony in Mexico.
